headline.print_headline: Tight Divisional Races Loom in Race for AL Pennant
headline.main: Tight Divisional Races Loom in Race for AL Pennant

lead_paragraph: Competition should be keen given the prospects of tight division races that could provide another nail-biting season's finish when American League baseball action gets under way on March 31.
